    "client_msg_id": "885086ea-35f6-4cc8-827f-99a1861926c8",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Interesting thought.\n\nIn a sense things like Github do a job of providing some web annotations to a code base, but it could be done at a finer-grained level with actual annotations to the code itself, not IN the code, but in the github page about it.\n\nOr not necessarily github you could put it into any web front-end to git.",
